Package cards

Contains the classes that deal with cards and decks in Cards Against Humanity.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnswerCard
    A type object that represents an answer card (The white cards in Cards Against Humanity).
    Card
    A type object that represents a card.
    CardHistory
    A class of object that stores data about the history of different CAH cards.
    Deck
    A type of object that represents a set of two decks.
    DeckBuilder
    An object that creates decks.
    Hand
    An object that represents a hand of cards.
    QuestionCard
    A type object that represents a question card (The black cards in Cards Against Humanity).
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Decks
    An enum that holds information about each deck.
    Tag
    An enum that contains all of the AnswerCards' tags.

Package cards Description

Contains the classes that deal with cards and decks in Cards Against Humanity. Work on card importing from text files.
Since:
CAH1.0
Version:
CAH1.0
Author:
Holt Maki
